<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/24871100">读史时，哪些故事让你动容？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2130402" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">让人唏嘘感叹亦可，让人肃然起敬亦可，让人心头一暖亦可，让人会心一笑亦可</div>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-meta zm-item-comment-el clearfix" id="zh-question-meta-wrap">
