<div class="answer-head">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730"
class="zm-item-link-avatar"
href="/people/kaiserwang730">
<img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg"
class="zm-list-avatar"
data-source="//pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg" />
</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="118">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$ou-yang-ying-61" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/ou-yang-ying-61" class="zg-link" title="欧阳颖">欧阳颖</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$sun-wen-89-10" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/sun-wen-89-10" class="zg-link" title="Steven">Steven</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$tang-tang-19-32-57" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/tang-tang-19-32-57" class="zg-link" title="汤汤">汤汤</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2130402" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">公元360年，前燕皇帝慕容隽总在噩梦中见到后赵暴君石虎。<br><br>慕容隽挖出了石虎的尸体，鞭尸，扔进了漳河。<br><br>公元370年，王猛灭亡前燕，重新葬了石虎。<br><br>石虎的尸体就那么在漳河里泡了十年。


</div>

</div>
