<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$shen-yuan-luo-niao" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/shen-yuan-luo-niao" class="zg-link" title="深淵落鳥">深淵落鳥</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$hai-mian-mian-80" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/hai-mian-mian-80" class="zg-link" title="海绵绵">海绵绵</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$liu-qi-41" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/liu-qi-41" class="zg-link" title="刘祺">刘祺</a></span>
